<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='156:182'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-1a' );" name="012-1a" class="pb">[012-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='182:190'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='190:200'>　周禮句解卷十二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='200:221'>　　　　　　　　　　　　　宋　朱申　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='221:232'>　　　冬官考工記下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='232:268'>玉人之事<span class='krp-note'>攻玉之工/玉人為長</span>鎭圭尺有二寸天子守之<span class='krp-note'>鎭取鎭/安四方</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='268:306'>　<span class='krp-note'>之/義</span>命圭九寸謂之桓圭公守之<span class='krp-note'>公侯伯之圭皆曰命/者以其出於王所命</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='306:343'>　<span class='krp-note'>也桓取强直/有立之義</span>命圭七寸謂之信圭侯守之<span class='krp-note'>信取尊而/不屈之義</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='343:382'>　<span class='krp-note'>信/申</span>命圭七寸謂之躬圭伯守之<span class='krp-note'>躬取卑而不信之義/  以上制度詳見大</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='382:408'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-1b' );" name="012-1b" class="pb">[012-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='408:447'>　<span class='krp-note'>宗伯/注</span>天子執冒四寸<span class='krp-note'>冒圭其形四方其大四寸/邪刻其下取覆冒為義</span>以朝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='447:490'>　諸侯<span class='krp-note'>諸侯來朝則以其瑞圭銳首上合/於天子之冒圭以為驗也朝潮同</span>天子用全<span class='krp-note'>此/言</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='490:535'>　<span class='krp-note'>祼圭也祼圭一器有瓉有龍/有將惟天子則全用玉為之</span>上公用龍<span class='krp-note'>祼圭以龍為/首上公之祼</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='535:578'>　<span class='krp-note'>圭以玉飾其/首故曰用龍</span>侯用瓚<span class='krp-note'>祼圭盛鬯處曰瓚侯之祼/圭以玉飾瓚故曰用瓚</span>伯用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='578:619'>　將<span class='krp-note'>祼圭之柄曰將伯之祼圭/以玉飾其柄故曰用將</span>繼子男執皮帛<span class='krp-note'>此上疑/有脫文</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='619:663'>　<span class='krp-note'>典命曰凡諸侯之適子未誓/則以皮帛繼子男詳見本注</span>天子圭中必<span class='krp-note'>必與縪同/謂以維約</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='663:702'>　<span class='krp-note'>其圭之中央/防失墜也</span>四圭尺有二寸以禮天<span class='krp-note'>典瑞曰四圭有/邸以祀天旅上</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='702:742'>　<span class='krp-note'>帝/</span>大圭長三尺<span class='krp-note'>典瑞曰王/搢大圭</span>杼上終葵首<span class='krp-note'>杼殺也終葵/推也為推於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='742:768'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-2a' );" name="012-2a" class="pb">[012-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='768:807'>　<span class='krp-note'>其杼上明無所/屈也杼直吕反</span>天子服之<span class='krp-note'>服之則所/謂搢之也</span>土圭尺有五寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='807:844'>　以致曰以土地<span class='krp-note'>致日度日景也典瑞曰土圭以/致四時日月封國則以土地</span>祼圭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='844:875'>　尺有二寸有瓚以祀廟<span class='krp-note'>典瑞曰以肆先/王以祼賓客</span>琬圭九寸而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='875:911'>　繅以象徳<span class='krp-note'>繅藉玉者也典瑞曰以治徳/以結好也琬音宛繅音早</span>琰圭九寸判</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='911:950'>　規以除慝以易行<span class='krp-note'>判半也規半以上剡至首規半以/下為琢節也餘並見典瑞注琰音</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='950:992'>　<span class='krp-note'>冉易/去聲</span>璧羨度尺<span class='krp-note'>典瑞曰璧羨以/起度羨以善切</span>好三寸以為度<span class='krp-note'>好璧/孔也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='992:1038'>　<span class='krp-note'>其徑三寸圓者徑一而圍三則其肉之圍凡九寸矣/以徑三寸加圍九寸則得十一寸羡其三寸以為度</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='1038:1073'>　<span class='krp-note'>則盈一尺/矣好去聲</span>圭璧五寸以祀日月星辰<span class='krp-note'>見典/瑞注</span>璧琮九寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='1073:1099'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-2b' );" name="012-2b" class="pb">[012-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='1099:1135'>　諸侯以享天子<span class='krp-note'>圓曰璧方曰琮璧以帛琮/以錦蓋諸伯享天子之禮</span>穀圭七寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='1135:1172'>　天子以聘女<span class='krp-note'>典瑞曰以和/難以聘女</span>大璋中璋九寸<span class='krp-note'>半圭曰璋/曰大曰中</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='1172:1213'>　<span class='krp-note'>則知中璋小於大璋/矣其璋則皆九寸</span>邉璋七寸<span class='krp-note'>邉璋又小於中/璋其長七寸</span>射四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='1213:1259'>　寸<span class='krp-note'>其廣四寸射/音石下並同</span>厚寸<span class='krp-note'>其厚/一寸</span>黄金勺<span class='krp-note'>三璋皆璋瓚故有/勺以盛黄流以黄</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='1259:1304'>　<span class='krp-note'>金為/之</span>青金外<span class='krp-note'>以青金/飾其外</span>朱中<span class='krp-note'>以朱飾/其中</span>鼻寸<span class='krp-note'>鼻謂龍頭/其高一寸</span>衡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='1304:1347'>　四寸<span class='krp-note'>勺之徑/廣四寸</span>有繅<span class='krp-note'>所以/藉璋</span>天子以巡守<span class='krp-note'>天子巡守所過/有事於山川視</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='1347:1391'>　<span class='krp-note'>山川之三等而/用二璋也守狩</span>宗祝以前馬<span class='krp-note'>宗宗伯之屬祝太祝之/屬天子巡守則宗祝以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='1391:1432'>　<span class='krp-note'>此前馬/而致禮</span>大璋亦如之<span class='krp-note'>言諸侯之大璋亦如邉/璋之長七寸射四寸者</span>諸侯以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='1432:1458'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-3a' );" name="012-3a" class="pb">[012-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1458:1490'>　聘女<span class='krp-note'>言天子用穀圭/諸侯用大璋也</span>瑑圭璋八寸璧琮八寸以頫聘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1490:1531'>　<span class='krp-note'>見典瑞注瑑/篆頫工弔反</span>牙璋中璋七寸<span class='krp-note'>中璋牙璋/之小者</span>射二寸<span class='krp-note'>廣二/寸</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1531:1568'>　厚寸<span class='krp-note'>厚一/寸</span>以起軍旅以治兵守<span class='krp-note'>見典/瑞注</span>駔琮五寸<span class='krp-note'>駔與/組同</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1568:1610'>　<span class='krp-note'>言係之以/組也駔祖</span>宗后以為權<span class='krp-note'>宗后即王后也以組係/琮為稱錘以權輕重也</span>大琮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1610:1646'>　十有二寸<span class='krp-note'>大於五寸七寸/之琮故曰大琮</span>射四寸厚寸是謂内鎭<span class='krp-note'>大/琮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1646:1689'>　<span class='krp-note'>為内鎮以見鎮/圭之為外鎮也</span>宗后守之<span class='krp-note'>猶王之守/鎮圭也</span>駔琮七寸<span class='krp-note'>宗后/五寸</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1689:1726'>　<span class='krp-note'>而天子七寸者/隆殺之辨也</span>鼻寸有半寸<span class='krp-note'>宗后之制/亦如此</span>天子以為權</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1726:1760'>　<span class='krp-note'>以權/輕重</span>兩圭五寸有邸以祀地以旅四望<span class='krp-note'>見典瑞/注邸抵</span>瑑琮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1760:1786'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-3b' );" name="012-3b" class="pb">[012-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1786:1827'>　八寸<span class='krp-note'>以别於禮神/故加琢刻也</span>諸侯以享夫人<span class='krp-note'>諸侯相為賓則夫/人有致禮之儀則</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1827:1865'>　<span class='krp-note'>享夫人者亦/施報之禮也</span>案十有二寸<span class='krp-note'>以玉飾案其/髙十二寸</span>棗㮚十有二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1865:1905'>　列<span class='krp-note'>以棗㮚陳於案上/為十二列也㮚栗</span>諸侯純九<span class='krp-note'>以勞諸侯/皆用九列</span>大夫純五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1905:1948'>　<span class='krp-note'>以勞大夫/皆用五列</span>夫人以勞諸侯<span class='krp-note'>夫人謂天子之三夫人也/夫人佐后治内政故王勞</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1948:1994'>　<span class='krp-note'>賔客而夫人亦以棗栗勞之隂陽相成之義也然諸/侯純九大夫純五者則知所謂十二列者勞二王之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1994:2029'>　<span class='krp-note'>後也勞/去聲</span>璋邸射素功以祀山川以致稍餼<span class='krp-note'>典瑞曰以/祀山川以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='2029:2064'>　<span class='krp-note'>造贈賔客素功者不加琢飾也所謂致/稍餼者即造贈賔客之謂也稍去聲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='2064:2072'>楖人<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='2072:2098'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-4a' );" name="012-4a" class="pb">[012-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='2098:2106'>雕人<span class='krp-note'>闕/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='2106:2129'>磬氏為磬倨句一矩有半其愽為一股為二鼔為三參</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='2129:2152'>　分其股愽去一以為鼓愽參分其鼓愽以其一為之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='2152:2168'>　厚已上則摩其旁已下則摩其耑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='2168:2195'>矢人為矢<span class='krp-note'>矢箭/也</span>鍭矢參分茀矢參分一在前二在後兵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='2195:2218'>　矢田矢五分二在前三在後殺矢七分三在前四在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='2218:2241'>　後參分其長而殺其一五分其長而羽其一以其笴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='2241:2264'>　厚為之羽深水之以辨其隂陽夾其隂陽以設其比</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='2264:2290'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-4b' );" name="012-4b" class="pb">[012-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='2290:2313'>　夾其比以設其羽參分其羽以設其刄則雖有疾風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='2313:2336'>　亦弗之能憚矣刄長寸圍寸鋌十之重三垸前弱則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='2336:2377'>　俛<span class='krp-note'>前弱則矢/行而低</span>後弱則翔<span class='krp-note'>後弱則矢/行而還</span>中弱則紆<span class='krp-note'>中弱則/矢行而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='2377:2419'>　<span class='krp-note'>曲/</span>中强則揚<span class='krp-note'>中强則矢行而起此四/者强弱之失其中也</span>羽豐則遲<span class='krp-note'>羽多/則矢</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='2419:2463'>　<span class='krp-note'>重而其行/失於緩</span>羽殺則趮<span class='krp-note'>羽少則矢輕而其行失於急此/二者豐殺之失其節也殺去聲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='2463:2500'>　<span class='krp-note'>趮/躁</span>是故夾而搖之<span class='krp-note'>此言相矢之法言宜/以指夾矢而搖之</span>以眡其豐殺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='2500:2539'>　之節也<span class='krp-note'>以矢之輕重而/知其豐殺之節</span>撓之<span class='krp-note'>以指撓其/榦而曲之</span>以眡其鴻殺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='2539:2572'>　之稱也<span class='krp-note'>以矢之强弱而知其/鴻殺之稱稱去聲</span>凡相笴欲生而搏同搏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='2572:2598'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-5a' );" name="012-5a" class="pb">[012-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='2598:2612'>　欲重同重節欲疏同疏欲㮚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='2612:2635'>陶人為甗實二鬴厚半寸脣寸盆實二鬴厚半寸脣寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='2635:2658'>　甑實二鬴厚半寸脣寸七穿鬲實五觳厚半寸脣寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='2658:2670'>　庾實二觳厚半寸脣寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='2670:2693'>旊人為簋實一觳崇尺厚半寸脣寸豆實三而成觳崇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='2693:2716'>　尺凡陶瓬之事髺墾薜暴不入市器中膞豆中縣膞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='2716:2725'>　崇四尺方四寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='2725:2764'>梓人為筍簴<span class='krp-note'>筍簴鍾磬之架也横/曰筍直曰簴簴音巨</span>天下之大獸五<span class='krp-note'>其目/在下</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='2764:2790'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-5b' );" name="012-5b" class="pb">[012-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2790:2835'>　脂者<span class='krp-note'>牛羊/之屬</span>膏者<span class='krp-note'>犬豕/之屬</span>臝者<span class='krp-note'>虎豹之屬以其體重毛/淺猶祼袒也臝力果反</span>羽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2835:2874'>　者<span class='krp-note'>飛禽/之屬</span>鱗者<span class='krp-note'>龍蛇/之屬</span>宗廟之事<span class='krp-note'>五獸用/於宗廟</span>脂者膏者以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2874:2911'>　牲<span class='krp-note'>致美/味也</span>臝者羽者鱗者以為筍簴<span class='krp-note'>貴野/聲也</span>外骨<span class='krp-note'>龜/屬</span>内骨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2911:2960'>　<span class='krp-note'>鱉/屬</span>郤行<span class='krp-note'>若蚓/之類</span>仄行<span class='krp-note'>若蠏/之類</span>連行<span class='krp-note'>若魚/之類</span>紆行<span class='krp-note'>若蛇之類/紆乙俱反</span>以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2960:2999'>　脰鳴者<span class='krp-note'>蛙黽之/屬脰豆</span>以注鳴者<span class='krp-note'>蟋蟀/之類</span>以旁鳴者<span class='krp-note'>蜩蜺/之屬</span>以翼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2999:3037'>　鳴者<span class='krp-note'>發皇/之屬</span>以股鳴者<span class='krp-note'>斯螽/之屬</span>以胷鳴者<span class='krp-note'>榮原/之屬</span>謂之小蟲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='3037:3079'>　之屬<span class='krp-note'>骨者二行者四鳴/者六皆小蟲之屬</span>以為雕琢<span class='krp-note'>凡此皆雕琢其/形而飾筍簴也</span>厚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='3079:3102'>　脣弇口出目短耳大胷燿後大體短脰若是者謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='3102:3128'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-6a' );" name="012-6a" class="pb">[012-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='3128:3151'>　臝屬恒有力而不能走其聲大而宏有力而不能走</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='3151:3174'>　則於任重宜聲大而宏則於鍾宜若是者以為鍾虡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='3174:3197'>　是故擊其所縣而由其虡鳴鋭啄決吻數目顅脰小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='3197:3220'>　體騫腹若是者謂之羽屬恒無力而輕其聲清揚而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='3220:3243'>　逺聞無力而輕則於任輕宜其聲清揚而逺聞於磬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='3243:3266'>　宜若是者以為磬虡故擊其所縣而由其虡鳴小首</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='3266:3289'>　而長搏身而鴻若是者謂之鱗屬以為筍凡攖閷援</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='3289:3312'>　簭之類必深其爪出其目作其鱗之而深其爪出其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='3312:3338'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-6b' );" name="012-6b" class="pb">[012-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='3338:3361'>　目作其鱗之而則於眡必撥爾而怒苟撥爾而怒則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='3361:3384'>　於任重宜且其匪色必似鳴矣爪不深目不出鱗之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='3384:3407'>　而不作則必穨爾如委矣苟穨爾如委則加任焉則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='3407:3423'>　必如將廢措其匪色必似不鳴矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='3423:3446'>梓人為飲器勺一升爵一升觚三升獻以爵而酬以觚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='3446:3469'>　一獻而三酬則一豆矣食一豆肉飲一豆酒中人之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='3469:3489'>　食也凡試梓飲器鄉衡而實不盡梓師罪之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='3489:3528'>梓人為侯<span class='krp-note'>侯今之/射垜也</span>廣與崇方<span class='krp-note'>崇高也方猶等也高/廣等者謂侯中也</span>參分</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='3528:3554'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-7a' );" name="012-7a" class="pb">[012-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='3554:3598'>　其廣<span class='krp-note'>天子射禮以九為節侯道九十弓弓二寸以為/侯中高廣等則天子侯中丈八尺諸侯於其國</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='3598:3642'>　<span class='krp-note'>亦/然</span>而鵠居一焉<span class='krp-note'>鵠所射也以皮為之各如其侯也居/侯中參分之一則此鵠方六尺惟大</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='3642:3678'>　<span class='krp-note'>射以皮飾侯大射者將祭/之射也其餘有賔射燕射</span>上兩个與其身三下兩个</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='3678:3722'>　半之<span class='krp-note'>兩个謂布可以維持侯者也上方兩枚與身三/設身廣一丈兩个各一丈凡為三丈下兩个半</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='3722:3760'>　<span class='krp-note'>之傳地/故短也</span>上綱與下綱出舌尋縜寸焉<span class='krp-note'>綱所以繫侯於/植者也舌維持</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='3760:3798'>　<span class='krp-note'>侯者上下皆出舌一尋者亦人張/手之節也縜籠綱者縜尤粉反</span>張皮侯而棲鵠則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='3798:3841'>　春以功<span class='krp-note'>鵠射之的也張皮侯而棲鵠謂以皮飾侯而/用於大射也諸侯以春貢士天子因大射而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='3841:3881'>　<span class='krp-note'>選士助祭取其中/的之功也春上聲</span>張五采之侯則逺國屬<span class='krp-note'>五采侯猶/今之紅心</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='3881:3907'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-7b' );" name="012-7b" class="pb">[012-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='3907:3952'>　<span class='krp-note'>蓋朱其中白次之蒼次之黄次之黒居外也天子張/五采侯以行賔射之禮所以象文徳也故逺國屬</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='3952:3990'>　張獸侯則王以息燕<span class='krp-note'>獸侯畫為熊麋鹿豕虎豹之象/也天子張獸侯以用之燕射所</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='3990:4031'>　<span class='krp-note'>以示其為民除害也故/可以休息而安燕焉</span>祭侯之禮<span class='krp-note'>將射則先/祭侯之神</span>以酒脯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='4031:4075'>　醢<span class='krp-note'>不用牲/也醢海</span>其辭曰<span class='krp-note'>祭侯之/祝辭也</span>惟若寧侯<span class='krp-note'>若汝也寕安也/侯之為物捍内</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='4075:4117'>　<span class='krp-note'>蔽外以禦敵為任者也有諸侯之象焉故假/以為戒敕諸侯之辭言汝當安為諸侯也</span>毋或若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='4117:4155'>　女不寧侯<span class='krp-note'>此若字訓如蓋責之曰汝等諸侯/毋如此等不寕之侯毋無女汝</span>不屬於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='4155:4196'>　王所<span class='krp-note'>以其不寧故不服/屬於天子之所</span>故抗而射女<span class='krp-note'>數其不屬於王/之罪故立其侯</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='4196:4234'>　<span class='krp-note'>而射/之也</span>强飲强食<span class='krp-note'>此祝神之辭勉之/使飲食也强上聲</span>詒汝曾孫諸侯百</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='4234:4260'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-8a' );" name="012-8a" class="pb">[012-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='4260:4287'>　福<span class='krp-note'>汝侯既飲食醉飽當以百/福遺汝曽孫之為諸侯也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='4287:4323'>廬人為廬器<span class='krp-note'>謂戈㦸殳矛/之柄也廬盧</span>戈柲六尺有六寸<span class='krp-note'>柲猶/柄也</span>殳長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='4323:4357'>　尋有四尺<span class='krp-note'>八尺曰/尋殳殊</span>車㦸常<span class='krp-note'>倍尋/曰常</span>酋矛常有四尺夷矛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='4357:4396'>　三尋<span class='krp-note'>酋夷長短名/酋在由反</span>凡兵無過三其身<span class='krp-note'>八尺為一尋人/長八尺三其人</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='4396:4439'>　<span class='krp-note'>身之長則/三尋矣</span>過三其身<span class='krp-note'>設使過於/三尋之身</span>弗能用也<span class='krp-note'>則兵太長/不可得而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='4439:4480'>　<span class='krp-note'>用/之</span>而無已<span class='krp-note'>而又不止於/弗能用也</span>又以害人<span class='krp-note'>適所以為/人之害也</span>故攻國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='4480:4519'>　之兵欲短<span class='krp-note'>凡兵用之於攻/敵者則貴乎短</span>守國之兵欲長<span class='krp-note'>用之於守/城者則貴</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='4519:4562'>　<span class='krp-note'>乎/長</span>攻國之人衆<span class='krp-note'>此覆解欲短欲長之意/謂攻國者用人必多</span>行地逺<span class='krp-note'>其所/行之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='4562:4588'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-8b' );" name="012-8b" class="pb">[012-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='4588:4630'>　<span class='krp-note'>地又/甚逺</span>食飲飢<span class='krp-note'>飲食不時/故多飢也</span>且涉山林之阻<span class='krp-note'>又況跋涉山/林之險阻</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='4630:4668'>　是故兵欲短<span class='krp-note'>有此四者皆不便於/長兵故兵欲短也</span>守國之人寡<span class='krp-note'>守國/者用</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='4668:4710'>　<span class='krp-note'>人必/少</span>食飲飽<span class='krp-note'>飲食及時/故皆飽也</span>行地不逺<span class='krp-note'>雖徃來巡警/而所行不逺</span>且不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='4710:4749'>　涉山林之阻<span class='krp-note'>又况不跋涉/山林之險阻</span>是故兵欲長<span class='krp-note'>有此四者可/用長兵故兵</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='4749:4776'>　<span class='krp-note'>欲長/也</span>凡兵句兵欲無彈刺兵欲無蜎是故句兵椑刺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='4776:4799'>　兵搏擊兵同强舉圍欲細細則校刺兵同强舉圍欲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='4799:4822'>　重重欲傅人傅人則宻是故侵之凡為殳五分其長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='4822:4845'>　以其一為之被而圍之參分其圍去一以為晉圍五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='4845:4871'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-9a' );" name="012-9a" class="pb">[012-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='4871:4894'>　分其晉圍去一以為首圍凡為酋矛參分其長二在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='4894:4917'>　前一在後而圍之五分其圍去一以為晉圍參分其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='4917:4940'>　晉圍去一以為刺圍凡試廬事置而搖之以眡其蜎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='4940:4963'>　也灸諸牆以眡其橈之均也横而搖之以眡其勁也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='4963:4978'>　六建既備車不反覆謂之國工</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='4978:5020'>匠人建國<span class='krp-note'>前經謂惟王建國/辨方正位者此也</span>水地以縣<span class='krp-note'>先於四角立植/以繩垂之而墜</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='5020:5068'>　<span class='krp-note'>取其端直然後置水於/地而取其平也縣音𤣥</span>置𣙗以縣<span class='krp-note'>𣙗謂立八尺之木/以為表也水地而</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='5068:5113'>　<span class='krp-note'>得其平則可以量日景矣故置𣙗於其中復/以繩垂之而墜欲其表之端直也𣙗魚列反</span>眡以景</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='5113:5139'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-9b' );" name="012-9b" class="pb">[012-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='5139:5177'>　<span class='krp-note'>言所以置𣙗者/將以眡日景也</span>為規識日出之景與日入之景<span class='krp-note'>此言/眡日</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='5177:5223'>　<span class='krp-note'>景之法以取東西也立八尺之表於地之平處日出/東方則景在表之西日入西方則景在表之東乃於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='5223:5269'>　<span class='krp-note'>其景之兩端畫而記之然後以繩貫於所立之表如/景之長就地一匝為一大規則所識日出日入之景</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='5269:5314'>　<span class='krp-note'>可以定東西矣東西既定乃以自東至西之長而/中屈之以量南北則南北亦可得而定矣識音志</span>晝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='5314:5354'>　參諸日中之景<span class='krp-note'>經乆猶恐南北之未正又參諸日中/之景焉冬至日行南陸景長一丈三</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='5354:5397'>　<span class='krp-note'>尺夏至日行北陸景短一/尺五寸此日中之景也</span>夜考之極星<span class='krp-note'>極星中星也/初昏之時見</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='5397:5442'>　<span class='krp-note'>於正南之位晝參夜/考則南北無不正矣</span>以正朝夕<span class='krp-note'>以日中之景正其朝/則地之中得矣以極</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='5442:5458'>　<span class='krp-note'>星正其夕則/天之中得矣</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='5458:5485'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-10a' );" name="012-10a" class="pb">[012-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='5485:5528'>匠人營國<span class='krp-note'>始作而立之謂之建/周圍而治之謂之營</span>方九里<span class='krp-note'>上公之國其城/方九里天子之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='5528:5571'>　<span class='krp-note'>城不宜如/是之狹也</span>旁三門<span class='krp-note'>城之四旁各為/三門共十二門</span>國中九經九緯<span class='krp-note'>國/中</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='5571:5616'>　<span class='krp-note'>之路縱者九塗為之經/横者九塗為之緯緯位</span>經涂九軌<span class='krp-note'>軌車轍跡也言經/涂之廣可容九車</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='5616:5660'>　<span class='krp-note'>徃來然王城之門既有十二則所謂九/經九緯九軌者皆當以十二為數也</span>左祖右社<span class='krp-note'>正/宫</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='5660:5703'>　<span class='krp-note'>在城之中其左為/宗廟其右為社稷</span>面朝後市<span class='krp-note'>其前為朝廷其後/為市井朝潮下同</span>市朝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='5703:5741'>　一夫<span class='krp-note'>朝者官吏所㑹市者商旅所聚必/一夫百畆之地然後足以容之</span>夏后氏世室</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='5741:5786'>　<span class='krp-note'>此言三代明堂之制/夏后氏號為世室也</span>堂脩二七<span class='krp-note'>夏后氏度以步堂脩/二七者謂其南北之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='5786:5829'>　<span class='krp-note'>深十四/步也</span>廣四脩一<span class='krp-note'>堂之廣益以四分脩之一則其/廣十七步有半矣廣去聲下同</span>五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='5829:5856'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-10b' );" name="012-10b" class="pb">[012-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='5856:5895'>　室三四步四三尺<span class='krp-note'>堂上有五室以象五行東北木室/東南火室西南金室西北水室其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='5895:5941'>　<span class='krp-note'>深皆三步其廣皆益以四尺也中央/土室其深四步其廣益以二尺也</span>九階<span class='krp-note'>南面三階/東西北面</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='5941:5985'>　<span class='krp-note'>各二階共/為九階</span>四旁兩夾忩<span class='krp-note'>毎室四户毎户夾/以兩忩共為八忩</span>白盛<span class='krp-note'>以蜃/灰堊</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='5985:6026'>　<span class='krp-note'>其牆壁/也盛成</span>門堂三之二<span class='krp-note'>門堂門側之堂也其深/廣比正堂有三分之二</span>室三之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='6026:6066'>　一<span class='krp-note'>門堂之室其深廣比/正室有三分之一</span>殷人重屋<span class='krp-note'>殷人號為重/屋重平聲</span>堂脩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='6066:6105'>　七尋<span class='krp-note'>商人度以尋一尋八尺/七尋則深五丈六尺也</span>堂崇三尺<span class='krp-note'>崇高/也</span>四阿重</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='6105:6149'>　屋<span class='krp-note'>言四方屋棟皆為/重屋故號重屋也</span>周人明堂<span class='krp-note'>明堂之内有世室有/重屋三代各舉其一</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='6149:6191'>　<span class='krp-note'>以名/之</span>度九尺之筵<span class='krp-note'>周人度以筵毎筵長/九尺度待咨反下同</span>東西九筵<span class='krp-note'>東/西</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='6191:6218'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-11a' );" name="012-11a" class="pb">[012-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='6218:6259'>　<span class='krp-note'>之廣為八/丈一尺</span>南北七筵<span class='krp-note'>南北之深為/六丈三尺</span>堂崇一筵<span class='krp-note'>其高/九尺</span>五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='6259:6301'>　室<span class='krp-note'>與夏/制同</span>凡室二筵<span class='krp-note'>毎室一/丈八尺</span>室中度以几<span class='krp-note'>度量也此總/言量地之法</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='6301:6339'>　<span class='krp-note'>一几/五尺</span>堂上度以筵<span class='krp-note'>一筵/九尺</span>宫中度以尋<span class='krp-note'>一尋/八尺</span>野度以步</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='6339:6372'>　<span class='krp-note'>一步/六尺</span>涂度以軌<span class='krp-note'>一軌/七尺</span>廟門容大扃七个闈門容小扃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='6372:6395'>　三个路門不容乗車之五个應門二徹三个内有九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='6395:6437'>　室<span class='krp-note'>路門之内/有九室</span>九嬪居之<span class='krp-note'>九嬪賛三夫人以佐后而/治内政故各居一室嬪頻</span>外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='6437:6479'>　有九室<span class='krp-note'>路門之外/亦有九室</span>九卿朝焉<span class='krp-note'>九卿賛三公以佐天子/而治外政故其入朝也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='6479:6518'>　<span class='krp-note'>亦各居/一室焉</span>九分其國以為九分<span class='krp-note'>一國之内畫為九/分猶井田之法也</span>九卿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='6518:6545'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-11b' );" name="012-11b" class="pb">[012-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='6545:6584'>　治之<span class='krp-note'>三孤六卿合為/九卿各治一分</span>王宫門阿之制五雉<span class='krp-note'>雉城上之/堞也五堵</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='6584:6624'>　<span class='krp-note'>為雉則長三丈高於一丈也阿棟也/門阿之制五雉則三丈之長者五也</span>宫隅之制七雉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='6624:6666'>　<span class='krp-note'>隅角也宫隅髙於門阿故為/七雉則一丈之長者七也</span>城隅之制九雉<span class='krp-note'>城隅髙/於宫隅</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='6666:6710'>　<span class='krp-note'>故為九雉則三/丈之長者九也</span>經涂九軌<span class='krp-note'>城中經涂/可容九車</span>環涂七軌<span class='krp-note'>環城/之涂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='6710:6745'>　<span class='krp-note'>可容/七車</span>野涂五軌<span class='krp-note'>野外之涂/可容五車</span>門阿之制以為都城之制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='6745:6782'>　<span class='krp-note'>都城王子弟所封之邑其城/如門阿之制則無過五雉也</span>宫隅之制以為諸侯之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='6782:6820'>　城制<span class='krp-note'>諸侯之城如宫隅之/制則無過七雉也</span>環涂以為諸侯經涂<span class='krp-note'>諸侯/經涂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='6820:6848'>　<span class='krp-note'>可容/七車</span>野涂以為都經涂<span class='krp-note'>都邑經涂/可容五車</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='6848:6875'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-12a' );" name="012-12a" class="pb">[012-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='6875:6917'>匠人為溝洫<span class='krp-note'>此篇載溝洫之制與遂人不同遂人以一/夫至萬夫言之則以相連屬而言也此以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='6917:6963'>　<span class='krp-note'>一井至一同言之則以開方之法而言之要之考工/記未必皆成周之制今各隨本文解之不必强為之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='6963:7005'>　<span class='krp-note'>説/也</span>耜廣五寸<span class='krp-note'>耜耒頭之金/也其廣五寸</span>二耜為耦<span class='krp-note'>兩耜相合/號為一耦</span>一耦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='7005:7058'>　之伐<span class='krp-note'>二耜合為一尺則所/伐之土廣一尺矣</span>廣尺深尺謂之<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0850' title='KR0850' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0850.png'/><span class='krp-note'><img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0850' title='KR0850' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0850.png'/>之廣/深皆一</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='7058:7117'>　<span class='krp-note'>尺則二耜之/所伐也<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0850' title='KR0850' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0850.png'/>捲</span>田首倍之<span class='krp-note'>一夫受田百畆其方百步田/首則加<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0850' title='KR0850' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0850.png'/>之方倍而為遂也</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='7117:7159'>　廣二尺深二尺謂之遂<span class='krp-note'>一夫之田其間有遂以/通水其廣深倍於<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0850' title='KR0850' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0850.png'/>也</span>九夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='7159:7195'>　為井<span class='krp-note'>九夫之田號為/一井其方一里</span>井間廣四尺深四尺謂之溝<span class='krp-note'>一/井</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='7195:7238'>　<span class='krp-note'>之田其間有溝以通/水其廣深倍於遂也</span>方十里為成<span class='krp-note'>百夫之田其方/十里號為一成</span>成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='7238:7265'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-12b' );" name="012-12b" class="pb">[012-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='7265:7300'>　間廣八尺深八尺謂之洫<span class='krp-note'>一成之田其間有洫以/通水其廣深倍於溝也</span>方</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='7300:7332'>　百里為同<span class='krp-note'>千夫之田其方/百里號為一同</span>同間廣二尋深二仞謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='7332:7383'>　澮<span class='krp-note'>一同之田其間有澮以通水其廣深/又倍於洫也仞與尋皆八尺仞音刃</span>專達於川<span class='krp-note'><img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0850' title='KR0850' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0850.png'/>/之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='7383:7428'>　<span class='krp-note'>水達於遂遂之水達於溝溝之水達於/洫洫之水達於澮澮之水則専達於川</span>各載其名<span class='krp-note'>又/以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='7428:7469'>　<span class='krp-note'>别其水之/所從也</span>凡天下之地埶<span class='krp-note'>泛言天下/地埶埶勢</span>兩山之間<span class='krp-note'>謂山/間之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='7469:7513'>　<span class='krp-note'>平/地</span>必有川焉<span class='krp-note'>水之源出於山至於/平地則會而為川焉</span>大川之上<span class='krp-note'>謂大川/之岸上</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='7513:7543'>　必有涂焉<span class='krp-note'>必有道路/以通徃來</span>凡溝逆地阞謂之不行水屬不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='7543:7566'>　理孫謂之不行梢溝三十里而廣倍凡行奠水磬折</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='7566:7593'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-13a' );" name="012-13a" class="pb">[012-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='7593:7623'>　以參伍欲為淵則句於矩凡溝必因水勢<span class='krp-note'>溝所以導/水不因水</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='7623:7664'>　<span class='krp-note'>勢之曲直則/其流易壅</span>防必因地勢<span class='krp-note'>防所以止水不因地勢/之高下則其隄易壞</span>善</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='7664:7702'>　溝者水漱之<span class='krp-note'>善為溝者水必漱齧/之而無所壅也漱瘦</span>善防者水淫之<span class='krp-note'>善/為</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='7702:7734'>　<span class='krp-note'>防者水必淫液/之而無所決也</span>凡為防廣與崇方其閷參分去一大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='7734:7765'>　防外閷凡溝防必一日先深之以為式<span class='krp-note'>凡制溝防必/有定式預先</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='7765:7806'>　<span class='krp-note'>一日/深之</span>里為式<span class='krp-note'>必合一里之/廣通計之</span>然後可以傳衆力<span class='krp-note'>有定法/而後可</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='7806:7834'>　<span class='krp-note'>以齊/衆志</span>凡任索約大汲其版謂之無任葺屋參分瓦屋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='7834:7864'>　四分困<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1038' title='KR1038' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1038.png'/>倉城逆牆六分堂涂十有二分竇其崇三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='7864:7891'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-13b' );" name="012-13b" class="pb">[012-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='7891:7902'>　尺牆厚三尺崇三之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='7902:7925'>車人之事半矩謂之宣一宣有半謂之欘一欘有半謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='7925:7938'>　之柯一柯有半謂之磬折</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='7938:7970'>車人為耒<span class='krp-note'>耒之為器其體/曲亦車人為之</span>庛長尺有一寸中直者三尺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='7970:7993'>　有三寸上句者二尺有二寸自其庛縁其外以至於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='7993:8016'>　首以弦其内六尺有六寸與步相中也堅地欲直庛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='8016:8057'>　<span class='krp-note'>土剛則欲直庛深入而/易推庛謂耒下前曲木</span>柔地欲句庛<span class='krp-note'>土之柔處/欲曲庛</span>直庛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='8057:8089'>　則利推句庛則利發<span class='krp-note'>解上/文</span>倨句磬折謂之中地<span class='krp-note'>中地/之耒</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='8089:8116'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-14a' );" name="012-14a" class="pb">[012-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='8116:8134'>　<span class='krp-note'>形之曲直地磬/之折乎庛音次</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='8134:8163'>車人為車<span class='krp-note'>為大車栢/車之工</span>柯長三尺愽三寸厚一寸有半五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='8163:8186'>　分其長以其一為之首轂長半柯其圍一柯有半輻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='8186:8209'>　長一柯有半其愽三三寸厚三之一渠三柯者三行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='8209:8247'>　澤者欲短轂<span class='krp-note'>澤為沮洳之地用/於行澤故利短轂</span>行山者欲長轂<span class='krp-note'>山為/險阻</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='8247:8285'>　<span class='krp-note'>之地用/長轂</span>短轂則利<span class='krp-note'>無却行/之失</span>長轂則安<span class='krp-note'>無倍任/之勞</span>行澤者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='8285:8327'>　反輮<span class='krp-note'>輮牙也以為/輪之固抱也</span>行山者仄輮<span class='krp-note'>反則裏之滑者在外/仄則仄其裏之堅者</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='8327:8354'>　<span class='krp-note'>相/依</span>反輮則易仄輮則完六分其輪崇以其一為之牙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='8354:8381'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-14b' );" name="012-14b" class="pb">[012-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='8381:8404'>　圍栢車轂長一柯其圍二柯其輻一柯其渠二柯者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='8404:8427'>　三五分其輪崇以其一為之牙圍大車崇三柯綆寸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='8427:8450'>　牝服二柯有三分柯之二羊車二柯有參分柯之一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='8450:8473'>　栢車二柯凡為轅三其輪崇參分其長二在前一在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='8473:8489'>　後以鑿其鈎徹廣六尺鬲長六尺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='8489:8528'>弓人為弓<span class='krp-note'>此弓/工也</span>取六材必以其時<span class='krp-note'>六材幹角筋膠絲漆/也非天時無以備隂</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='8528:8572'>　<span class='krp-note'>陽之和故取/之必以其時</span>六材既聚<span class='krp-note'>六材既/已合聚</span>巧者和之<span class='krp-note'>非工巧無/以全六材</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='8572:8612'>　<span class='krp-note'>之用故資巧/者以和之</span>幹也者以為逺也<span class='krp-note'>弓所以為逺者其力/在榦故榦以為逺</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='8612:8639'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-15a' );" name="012-15a" class="pb">[012-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='8639:8672'>　角也者以為疾也<span class='krp-note'>弓所以疾發者其勢/在角故角以為疾</span>筋也者以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='8672:8712'>　深也<span class='krp-note'>角榦資筋以為堅/忍以射則中深也</span>膠也者以為和也<span class='krp-note'>三者得膠/然後相合</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='8712:8748'>　<span class='krp-note'>以為/和</span>絲也者以為固也<span class='krp-note'>結而固之在絲/故絲所以為固</span>漆也者以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='8748:8781'>　受霜露也<span class='krp-note'>飾而堅之在漆故/漆所以為受霜露</span>凡取榦之道七柘為上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='8781:8805'>　檍次之檿桑次之橘次之木𤓰次之荆次之竹為下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='8805:8828'>　凡相榦欲赤黒而陽聲赤黒則鄉心陽聲則逺根凡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='8828:8851'>　析榦射逺者用勢深者用直居榦之道菑栗不迆則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='8851:8874'>　弓不發凡相角秋閷者厚春閷者薄穉牛之角直而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='8874:8901'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-15b' );" name="012-15b" class="pb">[012-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='8901:8924'>　澤老牛之角紾而昔疢疾險中瘠牛之角無澤角欲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='8924:8954'>　青白而豐末夫角之本蹙於<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1120' title='KR1120' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1120.png'/>而休於氣是故柔柔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='8954:8977'>　故欲其埶也白也者埶之徴也夫角之中恒當弓之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='8977:9000'>　畏畏也者必橈橈故欲其堅也青也者堅之徴也夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='9000:9030'>　角之未逺於<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1120' title='KR1120' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1120.png'/>而不休於氣是故脆脆故欲其柔也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='9030:9053'>　豐末也者柔之徴也角長二尺有五寸三色不失理</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='9053:9076'>　謂之牛戴牛凡相膠欲朱色而昔昔也者深瑕而澤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='9076:9099'>　紾而搏廉鹿膠青白馬膠赤白牛膠火赤鼠膠黒魚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='9099:9126'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-16a' );" name="012-16a" class="pb">[012-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='9126:9149'>　膠餌犀膠黄凡昵之類不能方凡相筋欲小簡而長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='9149:9172'>　大結而澤小簡而長大結而澤則其為獸必剽以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='9172:9195'>　弓則豈異於其獸筋欲敝之敝漆欲測絲欲沈得此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='9195:9226'>　六材之全然後可以為良凡為弓<span class='krp-note'>弓有六材而治/之各以其時</span>冬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='9226:9269'>　析榦<span class='krp-note'>榦欲堅而貞/固故冬析之</span>而春液角<span class='krp-note'>角欲和而温/柔故春液之</span>夏治筋<span class='krp-note'>筋/欲</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='9269:9314'>　<span class='krp-note'>散而解緩/故夏治之</span>秋合三材<span class='krp-note'>膠絲漆三者欲其成/就而充實故秋合之</span>寒奠體<span class='krp-note'>奠/定</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='9314:9360'>　<span class='krp-note'>也體者弓徃來之體也必於寒而/奠之則弓體用膠至冬堅而牢也</span>氷析灂<span class='krp-note'>灂者漆之/灂也必於</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='9360:9404'>　<span class='krp-note'>氷而析之則漆灂欲/其不動故也灂子召</span>冬析榦則易<span class='krp-note'>此覆解上文謂於/榦堅之時而析之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='9404:9431'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-16b' );" name="012-16b" class="pb">[012-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='9431:9471'>　<span class='krp-note'>則其勢和易/也易去聲</span>春液角則合<span class='krp-note'>於角和之時而液/之則其氣浹洽也</span>夏治筋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='9471:9511'>　則不煩<span class='krp-note'>於筋散之時而治/之則其理不亂也</span>秋合三材則合<span class='krp-note'>於成材之/時而合之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='9511:9549'>　<span class='krp-note'>則其質不/相離也</span>寒奠體則張不流<span class='krp-note'>體已定則雖張/之而不流移也</span>氷析灂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='9549:9586'>　則審環<span class='krp-note'>灂已環則不復/有所鼔動也</span>春被弦則一年之事<span class='krp-note'>被弦於/春俟一</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='9586:9616'>　<span class='krp-note'>朞之乆而/後可用也</span>析榦必倫析角無邪斵目必荼斵目不荼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='9616:9639'>　則及其大脩也筋代之受病夫目也者必强强者在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='9639:9662'>　内而摩其筋夫筋之所由幨恒由此作故角三液而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='9662:9685'>　榦再液厚其帤則木堅薄其帤則需是故厚其液而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='9685:9712'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-17a' );" name="012-17a" class="pb">[012-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='9712:9735'>　節其帤約之不皆約疏數必侔斵摯必中膠之必均</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='9735:9758'>　斵摯不中膠之不均則及其大脩也角代之受病夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='9758:9781'>　懷膠於内而摩其角夫角之所由挫恒由此作凡居</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='9781:9804'>　角長者以次需恒角而短是謂逆橈引之則縱釋之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='9804:9827'>　則不挍恒角而達譬如終紲非弓之利也今夫茭解</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='9827:9850'>　中有變焉故挍於挺臂中有柎焉故剽恒角而達引</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='9850:9873'>　如終紲非弓之利撟榦欲孰於火而無贏撟角欲孰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='9873:9896'>　於火而無燂引筋欲盡而無傷其力鬻膠欲孰而水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='9896:9923'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-17b' );" name="012-17b" class="pb">[012-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='9923:9946'>　火相得然則居旱亦不動居濕亦不動苟有賤工必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='9946:9969'>　因角榦之濕以為之柔善者在外動者在内雖善於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='9969:9992'>　外必動於内雖善亦弗可以為良矣凡為弓方其峻</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='9992:10015'>　而高其柎長其畏而薄其敝宛之無已應下柎之弓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='10015:10038'>　末應將興為柎而發必動於閷弓而羽閷末應將發</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='10038:10076'>　弓有六材焉<span class='krp-note'>六者之中榦/角為急用</span>惟榦强之<span class='krp-note'>弓以榦為强以/角附榦而安</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='10076:10113'>　張如水流<span class='krp-note'>張之如水/之順流</span>維體防之<span class='krp-note'>弓徃來之體防/其深淺之失</span>引之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='10113:10149'>　中參維角䟫之<span class='krp-note'>引弓與三尺之矢相中䟫/正也必其用角之正䟫棖</span>欲宛而無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='10149:10176'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-18a' );" name="012-18a" class="pb">[012-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='10176:10199'>　負弦引之如環釋之無失體如環材美工巧為之時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='10199:10230'>　謂之參均<span class='krp-note'>得天時材美/工巧為三均</span>角不勝榦榦不勝筋謂之參</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='10230:10267'>　均<span class='krp-note'>用榦勝一石如角勝二石被/筋勝三石三者皆平曰三均</span>量其力有參均均者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='10267:10305'>　參謂之九和<span class='krp-note'>合上材工時角榦筋之六者又以/絲漆膠為之輔九者相得而和</span>九和</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='10305:10339'>　之弓角與榦權<span class='krp-note'>角與榦/皆權平</span>筋三侔<span class='krp-note'>侔猶/等也</span>膠三鋝絲三邸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='10339:10377'>　漆三斞<span class='krp-note'>鋝相稱也邸相敵/也斞有所受也</span>上工以有餘<span class='krp-note'>巧工和之/而有餘</span>下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='10377:10406'>　工以不足<span class='krp-note'>下工和之/則不足</span>為天子之弓合九而成規為諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='10406:10429'>　侯之弓合七而成規大夫之弓合五而成規士之弓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='10429:10456'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-18b' );" name="012-18b" class="pb">[012-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='10456:10492'>　合三而成規<span class='krp-note'>説並見夏官/司弓矢註</span>弓長六尺有六寸<span class='krp-note'>此言人/之形貌</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='10492:10532'>　<span class='krp-note'>不同故弓之等制不一/六尺六寸弓之制長者</span>謂之上制<span class='krp-note'>此弓之/上等</span>上士服之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='10532:10571'>　<span class='krp-note'>士之上者/能用之</span>弓長六尺有三寸<span class='krp-note'>此得長短/之中者</span>謂之中制<span class='krp-note'>此/弓</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='10571:10609'>　<span class='krp-note'>之中/等</span>中士服之<span class='krp-note'>士之中者/能用之</span>弓長六尺<span class='krp-note'>弓之至/短者</span>謂之下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='10609:10643'>　制<span class='krp-note'>此弓之/下等</span>下士服之<span class='krp-note'>士之下者/能用之</span>凡為弓各因其君之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='10643:10666'>　躬志慮血氣豐肉而短寛緩以荼若是者為之危弓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='10666:10689'>　危弓為之安矢骨直以立忿執以奔若是者為之安</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='10689:10712'>　弓安弓為之危矢其人安其弓安其矢安則莫能以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='10712:10739'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-19a' );" name="012-19a" class="pb">[012-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='10739:10762'>　速中且不深其人危其弓危其矢危則莫能以愿中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='10762:10785'>　徃體多來體寡謂之夾臾之屬利射侯與弋徃體寡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='10785:10808'>　來體多謂之王弓之屬利射革與質徃體來體若一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='10808:10831'>　謂之唐弓之屬利射深大和無灂其次筋角皆有灂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='10831:10854'>　而深其次有灂而疏其次角無灂合灂若背手文角</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='10854:10884'>　環灂牛筋蕡灂麋筋斥蠖灂和弓<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0795' title='KR0795' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0795.png'/>摩覆之而角至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='10884:10923'>　謂之句弓<span class='krp-note'>詳察謂之覆極善謂之至角獨善/而筋榦未善謂之句弓弓之弊也</span>覆之而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='10923:10958'>　榦至謂之侯弓<span class='krp-note'>角善榦又善而筋獨未/善可以射侯謂之侯弓</span>覆之而筋至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='10958:10985'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0012', 'WYG', '012-19b' );" name="012-19b" class="pb">[012-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='10985:11015'>　謂之深弓<span class='krp-note'>非特角榦善而筋亦善故/疾而逺又中深故曰深弓</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='11015:11018'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='11018:11021'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='11021:11024'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='11024:11027'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='11027:11030'>　</span><br/>
